id: act1_02_questionnaire_genre

prompt:
  The tablet lights up with the first questionnaire screen. "What kind of
  experience would you like today?" Three soft-coloured buttons pulse beneath
  the prompt, waiting.

choice c_companionship:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Tap "Something gentle, with company."
  evidence: asked for a gentle, companionable experience on the questionnaire

choice c_mastery:
  tendency: control
  text: Tap "Something I can master — a system to learn."
  evidence: asked for a learnable, masterable system on the questionnaire

choice c_unsettle:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Tap "Something that doesn't flatter me."
  evidence: asked the lab not to flatter them on the questionnaire
